bowel and bladder control.

01:08:20.930 --> 01:08:22.725
And then I arrest you.

01:08:22.808 --> 01:08:24.350
Option two.
You tell me where

01:08:24.435 --> 01:08:26.770
John Biggs' drug lab is located.

01:08:26.854 --> 01:08:28.939
And then I arrest you.

01:08:29.689 --> 01:08:31.984
You have two seconds to decide.

01:09:40.761 --> 01:09:42.011
Totally justifiable.

01:09:42.179 --> 01:09:44.430
We are going to make
a lot of money.

01:09:44.598 --> 01:09:48.269
Nothing. No fear.
No increase in heart rate.

01:09:48.435 --> 01:09:51.772
No traces of anger whatsoever.

01:09:52.022 --> 01:09:54.358
Congratulations, Doctor.

01:09:54.692 --> 01:09:56.026
You did it.

01:09:57.278 --> 01:09:58.779
Yes, I did.

01:10:07.121 --> 01:10:08.414
<i>I told you, sir.</i>

01:10:08.581 --> 01:10:11.375
Norton clearly never had
control of the product.

01:10:11.542 --> 01:10:14.461
