01:19:37.357 --> 01:19:39.234
I know you remember me, Jerry.

01:19:43.280 --> 01:19:44.448
Where's Vallon?

01:19:44.531 --> 01:19:45.615
Wait a minute.

01:19:45.699 --> 01:19:48.179
