01:21:32.097 --> 01:21:33.265
Let's go. Go!

01:21:33.431 --> 01:21:34.766
All right, move! Let's go!

01:21:36.142 --> 01:21:37.978
Come on. Come on!

01:21:39.771 --> 01:21:40.772
Ready to go!

01:21:41.815 --> 01:21:43.149
They're all set.

